{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So there was no getting out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "One night, we went to sleep on the floor in this facility.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And a middle-aged couple, which were sort of pseudo grandparents-- I looked upon them as such-- we laid down together to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I was next to the woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in the morning when I woke up, they were both dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They had committed suicide during the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we woke up because the Germans were-- this is now the conquerors were opening the doors and shouting and coming up with, with pistols waving, and said, everybody out of here.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Everybody out of here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And as we pulled ourselves together, we heard a great deal of gunfire in the streets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we were actually-- my father was actually convinced that as we came out of the door, the stairs, there would be a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And it was just, just simply shoot everybody that would come out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And so we said a very emotional goodbye to each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we were fully aware of what would most likely would happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We went down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And amazingly enough, that was not it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "There were dead soldiers, dead horses, dead animals and people on the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But we were not being shot at.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And so we ducked down an alleyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And orders were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But nobody really knew which way to go or what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And so my father, together with another father and his family, we, we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we set out in the opposite direction of where the German soldiers wanted us to go and went into every farm that we passed and asked whether they would hide us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And the answers on all of them was, our barn is already full with refugees.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
